FT  04 OCT 94 / UK Company News: Porth losses
Losses at Porth Group, the USM-quoted decorations, packaging and framing
products concern, incurred increased pre-tax losses of Pounds 2.08m for the
first half of 1994, against Pounds 1.89m last time.
Turnover slipped to Pounds 2.11m (Pounds 2.2m) and interest charges were
Pounds 306,000 (Pounds 189,000). Losses per share came to 10.8p (9.8p).
